Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:16.29,comment,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs45\c&H00747C88\fad(2000,500)\fn@FZZJ-TTYBJW\b1\fsp5\frz-90\pos(570.801,132.666)}这样走下去该多好……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:30.31,comment,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs45\c&H00747C88\fad(2500,500)\fn@FZZJ-TTYBJW\b1\fsp5\frz-90\pos(605.467,263.333)}……到出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,槙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 大垣前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,基础练习结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,结果那孩子啊 把日期搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:09.93,comment,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLanTingHei-M-GBK\c&H00425867\bord0\fs75\pos(834,356)}标题方案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:11.43,comment,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLanTingHei-M-GBK\c&H00425867\bord0\fs75\pos(834,182)}标题方案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:23.94,comment,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLanTingHei-M-GBK\c&H00425867\bord0\an5\pos(730,258.4)\fs60\t(0,5000,\fs55)}标题方案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:23.94,comment,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLanTingHei-M-GBK\c&H00425867\bord0\fs56\t(\fs55)\pos(280.4,420)}『唯一知晓的你』
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,想睡的话就睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我会叫醒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很舍不得嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.49,0:22:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天就没睡多久 因为太期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.62,0:22:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是小孩子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样一直不叫醒她 似乎也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,…该换车了哦
